[{"id":805976,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"我特别在意 PWM 的调光模式<br />去店铺看了看 iPhone13 系列<br />iPhone13 mini 是肉眼可见的频闪<br />其他好一点 但也只是肉眼看不出来<br />而且一看到画面 眼球就开始发胀了<br /><br />参看了相关文章（太麻烦了 不贴了 勿喷） LED 的闪烁频率要到 3000Hz 以上才不会被眼球肌肉所感知<br />不然很有可能产生头晕 偏头疼 眼部干燥等症状 就算没有感知 这种频闪也是实实在在刺激到眼球肌肉了的<br /><br />更不要说 iPhone13 系列的 480hzPWM 调光模式了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805976","replies":74,"created_ts":1633428598,"created":"18:09:58","title":"iPhone 13 频闪真的不假 打算买 iPhone11 了","author":"hakufuasano","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hakufuasano","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f5effeaab08379dbb3396089d6d36b00?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":806003,"node":"Go 编程语言","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/go","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/f61d/6947/375_mini.png?m=1633234730","description":"<p>我大致搜了一下 go 开发的商城系统，基本上找不到，尤其是 go 开发的商业商城系统，反倒是 java，php 开发的商城系统和商业产品一大堆。cms 也是，这是为啥？</p>\n<p>是 go 的程序员不够多？还是 go 不适合做这些？不应该呀现在 go 的程序员也不少，go 的高并发也适合做商城类呀。</p>\n<p>求解</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/806003","replies":55,"created_ts":1633442737,"created":"22:05:37","title":"为什么网上 go 写的产品这么少","author":"zwgf","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zwgf","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bb63294db70af3e472f64d7ee5847dbd?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805929,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1633408415","description":"<p>我特意说明了主力机，原因是我只有一台，我在纳闷我更新后那些软件还能不能用，毕竟现在大部分软件下载页里的 window 包都是 win10 64/32 位和 win7 64/32 位</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805929","replies":44,"created_ts":1633403676,"created":"11:14:36","title":"win11 正式版今日推出，开发者你们的主力机都更新了吗？","author":"TangYuSen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/TangYuSen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/02fb25370e33db233e7b6ee0b54d9a9c?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805975,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1633408415","description":"Xeon E3-1230 v3 竟然不在支持列表里。。。。这是逼我升级电脑么。。。。我电脑还够用啊。。。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805975","replies":41,"created_ts":1633427491,"created":"17:51:31","title":"Win11 推送说不满足最低要求。。。。","author":"linuslv","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/linuslv","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5655/cf23/13782_mini.png?m=1404407353"},{"id":805963,"node":"硬件","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","description":"<p>亲戚的笔记本，联想 E480 最低配，无固态，因特殊原因，不能拆后盖，现在巨卡无比，硬盘长时间 100%，有什么办法能鼓捣一下？重装系统管用吗？外接一个移动固态硬盘可行吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805963","replies":40,"created_ts":1633420604,"created":"15:56:44","title":"机械硬盘，如何愉快用 Windows？","author":"hs0000t","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/hs0000t","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2363a2c5d942e5f44d98d88e652e7731?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805965,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>在此期间，照片不能被编辑，微信也发不出去。\n不是必现，摸不清规律，感觉像是做什么 hdr 优化，但也不能这么影响体验吧\n去年首发入手就有问题，已经一年了还不解决</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805965","replies":39,"created_ts":1633421136,"created":"16:05:36","title":"拍照后模糊，过一段时间才清晰。12/12mini 都遇到过","author":"haoyh1","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/haoyh1","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/1db3debddcb0b6aa2287ef70d1874277?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805915,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1633408415","description":"<p>微软之前宣布 10 月 5 号推送 win11，可我还是没有收到。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805915","replies":34,"created_ts":1633392596,"created":"08:09:56","title":"都收到 windows11 的推送了吗","author":"Pogbag","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Pogbag","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a49b/0fdd/300244_mini.png?m=1625492219"},{"id":805951,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"<p>女生用，现在用荣耀 10，3 年了，电池充电很热，最近想换。期望：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>排除苹果，不习惯苹果生态</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>价位 2599 ～ 3499</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>屏幕尽可能小，5.5-6.0 够了，屏幕太大不好拿。（看现在手机几乎都 6.0+，如果没有大一点就大一点吧）</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>不玩吃鸡王者，但玩恋与制作人这种，CPU 性能一般行了</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>rom 至少有 128g，建议有 256g，一般都满足吧？ ram6g ～ 8g 即可。拍照要求不高，极少拍照</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>不喜欢屏幕边沿弧度很弯的，直板手机即可。前摄像头形状在哪都没关系。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>希望有 40w+的快充</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>据了解，不喜欢某米、蓝绿厂其子品牌（排除这个我觉得已经减少 60%手机选择了，实在不行也可以推荐）</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>最主要一部分，是游戏账号问题，现在玩的游戏用的是华为账号，如果用蓝绿厂，能登回来原来的账号吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805951","replies":33,"created_ts":1633413685,"created":"14:01:25","title":"2021 下半年安卓手机求推荐","author":"oneisall8955","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/oneisall8955","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/60dc/c401/355824_mini.png?m=1632818428"},{"id":805938,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1633408415","description":"<p><img alt=\"图像\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://github.com/haoran213/Air_Pollution_Forcast_Beijing/blob/master/%E5%B1%8F%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE%202021-10-05%20120417.png?raw=true\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805938","replies":32,"created_ts":1633407685,"created":"12:21:25","title":"上午升级到了 11，终于用上 wsl-gpu 和 wslg 了，舒服了~~","author":"howthen","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/howthen","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/86550ccc5ef2789a40884f9b2186b40e?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805993,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","description":"<p>打算去小黄鱼收个 imac 体验下 5k 屏，17 款的 cpu 是 i5 7600 不知道还能撑几年\n价格在 8000 左右，不知道划算不？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805993","replies":28,"created_ts":1633437254,"created":"20:34:14","title":"现在买个 2017 款的 iMac 还能用几年","author":"dapolly","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/dapolly","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/861497af4aeeedc11c382438bcaa9005?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805927,"node":"Windows","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1633408415","description":"<p>不出意料的没收到更新推送，只好自己下载更新助手了。然后更新助手需要 Win11 升级检查的程序，一检查发现电脑没开 TPM 。打开 TPM 后开始更新。这下载安装速度确实比之前升级 Win10 的要快很多啊。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/4jYsVs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"4jYsVs.md.png\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/10/05/4jYsVs.md.png\"/></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://download.microsoft.com/download/3/a/9/3a9e2fe1-96e7-4514-8744-f3a9731f91c7/Windows11InstallationAssistant.exe\" rel=\"nofollow\">下载 Win11 更新助手</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://download.microsoft.com/download/5/b/4/5b4103b3-3135-4958-987d-3aba103333f6/3.1/X64/WindowsPCHealthCheckSetup.msi\" rel=\"nofollow\">下载 Win11 升级检查工具</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805927","replies":28,"created_ts":1633402927,"created":"11:02:07","title":"开始更新 Win11","author":"kdwycz","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/kdwycz","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5e08/74d6/71423_mini.png?m=1522317546"},{"id":805916,"node":"硬件","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/hardware","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9a11/5815/52_mini.png?m=1630576655","description":"<p>家里有一个玩客云改造的 nas. 但是风行电视装不上最新版的 kodi, 老版本的 emby 插件也装不上,折腾大半宿...\n想搞一个盒子, 然后安装 kodi+emby 插件方便连接 nas 上的动画片给娃娃看.电影连续剧给娃妈看...</p>\n<p>以上是基本需求, 额外需求是:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>如果能破解,安装各种黑科技 /白嫖资源的 app 更好啦.</li>\n<li>如果可玩性高一点就更好啦.</li>\n<li>便宜一点更好啦.</li>\n<li>有其他解决方案也更好啦.</li>\n</ul>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805916","replies":27,"created_ts":1633395755,"created":"09:02:35","title":"机顶盒求推荐...","author":"chaleaoch","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/chaleaoch","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/92e0/46b3/126993_mini.png?m=1622082563"},{"id":805940,"node":"Linux","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/linux","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6512/bd43/11_mini.png?m=1620106980","description":"<p>在基本处理后：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>关闭 root 登录</li>\n<li>关闭密码登录</li>\n<li>只允许密钥登录</li>\n<li>改 ssh 端口</li>\n</ol>\n<p>请问黑客在知道 ssh 端口的情况下，没有密钥，可以如何入侵服务器？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805940","replies":25,"created_ts":1633409030,"created":"12:43:50","title":"请教下老哥们，服务器安全问题","author":"akmisty","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/akmisty","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f6f6e6088ea1c9be5c161445f0e770ce?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805977,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"<p>之前没啥需求，用的罗技几十块钱的键盘鼠标套装，最近感觉鼠标越来越难用，还经常按的食指疼，所以想换个好点的鼠标，求推荐。五百以内都可以</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805977","replies":23,"created_ts":1633428674,"created":"18:11:14","title":"求推荐个无线鼠标，办公用","author":"Zzzsk8","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Zzzsk8","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/a0205ce5328e8549e303ca8642482342?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":805935,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1630643991","description":"<p>手机越来越失去便携的意义，摄像头厚重的不忍直视～一圈看下来兼顾性能重量的，似乎只有 iphone13 标准版和魅族 18 系列了……小米 /华为 /三星直接放弃，可选择的真不多</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/805935","replies":23,"created_ts":1633406582,"created":"12:03:02","title":"现在的旗舰机真是越来越厚重了～","author":"leonme","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/leonme","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/98b6e6a39a6c3f3aa7cd20709ab6c91f?s=24&d=retro"}]